data.description: Make your way to this beautiful farm style home nestled in the mountains of Florissant. This home can give you the best of both worlds in a quiet cul-de-sac. Enjoy your open concept fully remodeled kitchen, lovely cabinetry, stainless steal appliances and granite counter tops.  Then step out onto your deck over looking to the spectacular views of one of the twin rock formations. Great home with plenty of room to host family and friends. When you're ready to relax, step foot into the jetted tub in the master bath with a large window to enjoy your land. If you're an animal lover, enjoy peace and quiet with land and views. This is the property for you! 20 mins to Woodland Park, 45 mins to Colorado Springs this home has all the amenities needed for your convenience.
